additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: 98% of pregnant results were detected the day before the expected period, 97% 2 days before the expected period, 90% 3 days before and 65% 4 days before the expected period. ALWAYS READ THE LABEL AND FOLLOW THE DIRECTIONS FOR USE. For self-testing at home. For in vitro diagnostic use only. Do not reuse. Keep out of reach of children. Store between 2 - 30C. CAUTION: contains button batteries. Keep out of the reach of children. If swallowed or placed inside any part of the body, a button battery can cause serious injury. Seek immediate medical attention.
